Node Js should be downloaded
IDE (VS code) any code we can choose
Installation Using Command as npm Package
Create new folder and open in VS code
Click on open folder (Drag and Drop Folder in Vs Code)
Go to Terminal and run command -npm init playwright@latest
Need to give some question and answers
A-Do you want to use typescript or javascript B-Where to put end to end tests-Folder name C-Add a Github Action workflow-Y/N
Following will be added
Package.json-Node Project Mangement File
Playwright.config.js-Configuration File
Test Folder-Basic Example Test
Test-Examples Folder- Detailed Examples test
gitignore-to be used during git commit and push
playwright.yml-to be used during ci/cd pipeline
Check playwright added-npm playwright-v
Check playwright command option-npx playwright-h
